text: Laura Tidball-Balisky (born 2 March 1964) is a Canadian equestrian. She competed in the team jumping event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1987 Pan American Games Category:Sportspeople from Vancouver
